@startuml RxStateMachine
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam state {
  FontSize 12
  FontName Consolas
  BackgroundColor #E8F5E9
  BorderColor #2E7D32
}

title ISOTP Receiver FSM (HFSM2)
\n\n
state RxIdle : Waiting for first frame
state ReceiveSF : Single frame received
state ReceiveFF : First frame received, sending FC
state SendFC : Re-sending Flow Control
state ReceiveCF : Consecutive frame(s) expected
state RxCompleted : Message received complete
state RxError : Error state
\n\n
[*] --> RxIdle : Initial entry
\n\n
RxIdle --> ReceiveSF : RxFrame(SF) – store data immediately
RxIdle --> ReceiveFF : RxFrame(FF) – start reception
RxIdle --> RxError : RxFrame(other)
\n\n
ReceiveSF --> RxCompleted : Call onReceived, then auto
\n\n
ReceiveFF --> ReceiveCF : Send FC(CTS, BS, STmin), start N_Ar timer
ReceiveFF --> RxError : BufferOverflow (message too large)
\n\n
ReceiveCF --> RxCompleted : All CF received (len >= expectedLength), call onReceived
ReceiveCF --> ReceiveCF : More CF expected (re-enter to restart N_Cr timer)
ReceiveCF --> RxError : Invalid Sequence Number
ReceiveCF --> RxError : Timeout(N_Cr)
ReceiveCF --> RxError : RxFrame(other)
\n\n
SendFC --> ReceiveCF : Resend FC and go back to waiting CF
\n\n
RxCompleted --> RxIdle : auto
\n\n
RxIdle --> RxIdle : Reset
ReceiveFF --> RxIdle : Reset
ReceiveCF --> RxIdle : Reset
RxError --> RxIdle : Reset
\n\n
RxError --> RxError : any other event
\n\n
@enduml